comment.content: Cochin Airport is a small airport located in Nedumbassery, Kochi. Majority of  the international flights are to/from Middle East, East Asia and one going to London Gatwick. Check-in can be long if you are going on Qatar, Emirates or Air India. Security is organized compared to 2021. Indian Security requires you to remove all electronic devices including headphones and they do have extensive searches. Food can be a bit pricy according to Indian Standards. There are 5 gates in Terminal 3 and it can crowded during early morning hours as most middle eastern flights depart at that time. Immigration was a breeze. However all, Cochin Airport has a good , clean and spacious atmosphere.

destination.name: Kolkata Subhas Chandra Bose International Airport
